test_negate_of_divisors:
assert [] == [-1]
  Right contains one more item: -1
  Full diff:
  - [-1]
  + []
test_list_of_zeros:
assert [10, 20, 30] == [0]
  At index 0 diff: 10 != 0
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 20
  Full diff:
  - [0]
  + [10, 20, 30]
test_coefficient_of_divisor:
assert [12] == []
  Left contains one more item: 12
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [12]
